rhetorical device  
departure from what speakers of a particular language
apprehend to be the standard meaning of words, or the standard order of
words used to achieve some special meaning or effect, rhetorical devices
can be divided into rhetorical schemes (or figures) and rhetorical tropes.

rhetorical schemes  
